These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-1::.
Movie-Genre: romance, fantasy, zombie, comedy
Nationality: italian, nigerian, german, dutch
1. Movie-Genre:romance is on the right of Nationality:german##1
2. Nationality:dutch is on the far left##1
3. Nationality:german is between Nationality:nigerian and Movie-Genre:fantasy##2
4. Movie-Genre:comedy is on the far left##1
5. Movie-Genre:zombie is between Movie-Genre:fantasy and Movie-Genre:romance##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1       |    2    |    3     |     4      |
| Movie-Genre   | comedy         | fantasy   | zombie | romance       |
| Nationality      | dutch | italian | german   | nigerian |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-2::.
City: hannover, venice, miami, liverpool
Pet: frog, cat, hedgehog, chinchilla
1. Pet:chinchilla is between City:miami and Pet:cat##2
2. City:liverpool is on the far right##1
3. Pet:hedgehog is on the right of Pet:frog##1
4. City:hannover is on the left of Pet:frog##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2     |    3    |      4      |
| City         | venice | hannover | miami | liverpool |
| Pet   | cat    | chinchilla   | frog | hedgehog       |

