.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-3::.
Sport: swimming, handball, soccer, skateboarding
Movie-Genre: adventure, epic, mystery, action
1. Movie-Genre:mystery is on the right of Sport:skateboarding##1
2. Movie-Genre:mystery is between Movie-Genre:epic and Sport:handball##2
3. Movie-Genre:epic is on the far left##1
4. Movie-Genre:action is on the left of Sport:soccer##1
5. Sport:handball == Movie-Genre:action##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |   3    |     4      |
| Sport          | skateboarding    | swimming | handball   | soccer  |
| Movie-Genre   | epic | mystery   | action | adventure |

